com.thinkaurelius.titan.core.schema

Interface TitanSchemaElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Namifiable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    EdgeLabel, InternalRelationType, InternalVertexLabel, PropertyKey, RelationType, RelationTypeIndex, SystemRelationType, TitanGraphIndex, TitanIndex, TitanSchemaType, VertexLabel
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseKey, BaseLabel, BaseRelationType, BaseVertexLabel, EdgeLabelVertex, EmptyRelationType, ImplicitKey, PropertyKeyVertex, RelationTypeIndexWrapper, RelationTypeVertex, TitanGraphIndexWrapper, VertexLabelVertex

    public interface TitanSchemaElement
extends Namifiable
    Marks any element that is part of a Titan Schema. Titan Schema elements can be uniquely identified by their name.

    A Titan Schema element is either a TitanSchemaType or an index definition, i.e. TitanGraphIndex or RelationTypeIndex.

    Author:
    Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
